 and associated China rainfall anomalies. Scientia Meteor. Sinica, 28(2), 139-146. (in Chinese)Xu, C., Shen, X., Xu, Y., An analysis of climate change in East Asia by using the IPCC AR4 simulations (2007) Advances in Climate Change Research, 3 (5), pp. 287-292. , in Chinese; Zhao, Z., Yong, L., Advance on investigations of regional climate modeling since 1990 (1998) Acta Meteor. Sinica, 56 (2), pp. 225-246. , in Chinese; Zhou, T., Yu, R., 20th century surface air temperature over China and the globe simulated by coupled climate models (2006) J. Climate, 19 (22), pp. 5843-5858","Lin, M.; Nansen-Zhu International Research Center, Institute of Atmospheric Physics, Chinese Academy of Sciences, Beijing 100029, China; email: lmj@mail.iap.ac.cn",,,,,,,,08940525,,,,"English","Acta Meteorol. Sin.",Article,Scopus,2-s2.0-61349137509
